cs.DB, cs.LO, cs.AI, cs.DS, cs.CC. 

The paper deals with logical queries over views, which are a central topic in database research, and discusses their decidability and expressiveness. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.DB (Databases), followed by cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), as the paper deals with logical queries and ontology reasoning. Additionally, the paper involves some complexity analysis, which suggests the category cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.CC (Computational Complexity).
